    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Not only does a unit on the exit block unit movement  but a unit on the entrance will stop it from entering and buildings + terrain will stop a unit following the rally point as it tries to take the quickest route (straight) and becomes stuck. (steps to reproduce: place a building between the repair pad and its rallypoint ending).\n\nI noticed something very unique though, this rally point will cause the unit to actually displace every unit along the route UNLESS the other units came from the rally point. This is only attributed to the repair pad, all other rally points work as normal.\n"
